sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as FastAPI Router
    participant App as Application Service
    participant Domain as Domain Model
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events as Event System
    participant Metrics as Metrics Collector

    Client->>API: HTTP Request
    API->>API: Authentication & Validation
    API->>App: Execute Command/Query
    App->>Domain: Business Logic
    Domain->>Events: Publish Domain Event
    Events->>Metrics: Record Business Metrics
    App->>Repo: Persist Changes
    Repo->>DB: Database Operation
    DB-->>Repo: Result
    Repo-->>App: Success/Failure
    App-->>API: Result
    API->>API: Serialize Response
    API-->>Client: HTTP Response
